caption-attachment-124817\"\u003eThe alchemist\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThat also has an impact on progression and how much you can expand your base.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI have mostly spent time with melee combat, but there is a whole magic path to go down as well.  Plus there is archery, and done in a way I actually really like.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_124818\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_archery.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-124818\" data-attachment-id=\"124818\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/11/15/easing-into-enshrouded/es02_archery/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_archery.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1504,827\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES02_Archery\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Popping a hostile with arrows\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_archery.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_archery.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_archery.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"330\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_archery.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_archery.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_archery.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_archery.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_archery.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-124818\"\u003ePopping a hostile with arrows\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt also has a couple of special things, like the grappling hook, which is used to pull yourself up place or to swing across things.  You need to make one pretty early on as it gates some of the content.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_124820\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_grapplinghook.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-124820\" data-attachment-id=\"124820\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/11/15/easing-into-enshrouded/es02_grapplinghook/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_grapplinghook.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2143,1042\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES02_GrapplingHook\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Swinging across early in my venture\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_grapplinghook.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_grapplinghook.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_grapplinghook.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"292\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_grapplinghook.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_grapplinghook.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_grapplinghook.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_grapplinghook.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_grapplinghook.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-124820\"\u003eSwinging across early in my venture\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAnd then there is the glider… which true to its name lets you jump off of high places and glide across the landscape.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_124823\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_gliding.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-124823\" data-attachment-id=\"124823\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/11/15/easing-into-enshrouded/es02_gliding/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_gliding.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1767,909\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES02_Gliding\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Going for distance\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_gliding.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_gliding.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_gliding.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"309\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_gliding.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_gliding.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_gliding.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_gliding.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_gliding.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-124823\"\u003eGoing for distance\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThere is also the whole shrouded area, that foggy bit you see in the above image, where you can only stay for a specific duration.  I’ll probably get more into that, but I am feeling more like a breezy overview of things today.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBut mostly I think I like it because it is kind of pretty and fun to explore.  Some days that is all you need I guess.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_124828\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_prettysettlement.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-124828\" data-attachment-id=\"124828\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/11/15/easing-into-enshrouded/es02_prettysettlement/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_prettysettlement.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2860,1340\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES02_PrettySettlement\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Running into an abandoned settlement\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_prettysettlement.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_prettysettlement.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_prettysettlement.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_prettysettlement.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_prettysettlement.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_prettysettlement.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_prettysettlement.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_prettysettlement.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-124828\"\u003eRunning into an abandoned settlement\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn that way it is more like \u003cem\u003eConan Exiles\u003c/em\u003e, with a crafted world that is the same for everybody as opposed to the random world generation of \u003cem\u003eValheim\u003c/em\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGranted, the world isn’t done yet.  Potshot and I were out exploring and I had to ask if he also saw what appeared to be a translucent red wall off in the distance.  He did, so we went to explore it and, on stepping through it, received a dire warning.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_124826\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_redzone.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-124826\" data-attachment-id=\"124826\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/11/15/easing-into-enshrouded/es02_redzone/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_redzone.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1339,654\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES02_RedZone\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;You have nine seconds to comply!\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_redzone.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_redzone.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_redzone.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"293\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_redzone.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_redzone.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_redzone.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_redzone.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_redzone.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-124826\"\u003eYou have nine seconds to comply!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe had wandered to the edge of the early access area.  I wasn’t sure what it was going to do to me when the counter ran down, so I ran back out post haste.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSo yeah, no hiding the fact that we’re still in early access… though maybe the lack of in-game chat was the real hint on that front.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePotshot and I continued exploring, eventually finding another death trap that we glided directly into.  But at least the game puts your corpse marker… you have to go find that to pick up the stuff that was in your backpack with our current settings, though your equipped gear stays with you… on the edge of the place that killed you and not on the spot you eventually died on.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBut mostly it just looks good, which makes it inviting to carry on with.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_124819\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_fireatnight.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-124819\" data-attachment-id=\"124819\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/11/15/easing-into-enshrouded/es02_fireatnight/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_fireatnight.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2836,1310\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES02_FireAtNight\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;A bonfire at a hostile camp\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_fireatnight.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_fireatnight.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_fireatnight.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"277\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_fireatnight.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_fireatnight.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_fireatnight.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_fireatnight.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_fireatnight.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-124819\"\u003eA bonfire at a hostile camp\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe have barely gone far at all in the game.  There are a number of paths to follow, including the usual base building aspect that we often over-indulge in.  So there is lots to see still.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_124829\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_sunset.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-124829\" data-attachment-id=\"124829\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2024/11/15/easing-into-enshrouded/es02_sunset/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_sunset.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2860,1340\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"ES02_Sunset\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Enshrouded at sunset\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_sunset.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_sunset.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_sunset.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_sunset.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_sunset.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_sunset.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_sunset.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/es02_sunset.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-124829\"\u003eEnshrouded at sunset\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe have been wary of the shroud, the murky areas of the world in which it is hazardous to linger.  But we’ll get to that soon enough I am sure.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
